author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
We're back with The Indie Hour Episode Forty-Eight! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

When a leviathan of truly Lovecraftian proportions washes up on a nameless medieval shore, the folk around it descend into cult and eldritch madness. This diceless Diorama #28 Skirmish game lets you recreate the battles between the various cults that spring up in a Folk Horror arthouse game. Let's dive in!

Check out the Rulebook HERE: https://www.patreon.com/posts/132177380
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 048 - OMEN TIDE by Pawl Boracchi & Simon Schnitzler
